- Knopflerfish Servlet.jar (jsdk)
  
Used Paxle Bundles:
--------------------------------------------------   
- Paxle Core
- Paxle HttpTools
  
Used External Libraries:
--------------------------------------------------
- AC.lib-ICO: Java library for ICO files
  Files: aclibico-2.1.jar
  See: http://sourceforge.net/projects/aclibico/
